{"type":"message","id":"b95b34e6","parentId":"106a2419","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:42:40.145Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"openclaw-weixin:1776048155156-6d8b0de7\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-13 10:42 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\n1. ruishu-mcp (https://github.com/xuange520/ruishu-mcp)（⭐39）— API 网关/服务，支持远程调用\n2. webmcp (https://github.com/AuthBits/webmcp)（⭐97）— AI 服务平台，支持部署与任务管理\n3. my-claude-devteam (https://github.com/NYCU-Chung/my-claude-devteam)（⭐44）— 多智能体编排平台，支持协作与任务规划\n4. workflow-skill (https://github.com/twwch/workflow-skill)（⭐31）— 自动化工作流/编排工具，提升执行效率\n5. codex-tokens-compress (https://github.com/LuckyKuang/codex-tokens-compress)（⭐39）— 面向AI协作的AGENTS规约压缩实验仓库\n6. fireworks-tech-graph (https://github.com/yizhiyanhua-ai/fireworks-tech-graph)（⭐835）— 多智能体编排平台，支持协作与任务规划\n7. Crimson-Desert-Save-Editor-Mod-For-PC (https://github.com/12344466666666667777777777/Crimson-Desert-Save-Editor-Mod-For-PC)（⭐61）— 多代理模拟/仿真项目\n8. Free-FL-Studio-25.2.5-PC-Edition (https://github.com/suandimam/Free-FL-Studio-25.2.5-PC-Edition)（⭐52）— 自动化工作流/编排工具，提升执行效率\n9. wow-harness (https://github.com/NatureBlueee/wow-harness)（⭐38）— 面向 Agent 的技能生成与协作工具\n10. claude-code-setup (https://github.com/tomascortereal/claude-code-setup)（⭐35）— 自动化工作流/编排工具，提升执行效率"}],"timestamp":1776048160138}}
{"type":"message","id":"9937a74d","parentId":"b95b34e6","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:43:03.068Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 你这条里混了不少“看名字像相关、实际可能不靠谱”的仓库。\n\n如果你是要我**从这 10 个里筛出真正值得关注的 Agent / MCP / 工作流相关项目**，我建议先做一轮去噪，初判如下：\n\n**相对像正经相关项目的：**\n1. `ruishu-mcp` — 看名字像 MCP 服务/API 网关，值得看\n2. `webmcp` — 看名字像 MCP/AI 服务平台，值得看\n3. `my-claude-devteam` — 看名字像多智能体协作框架，值得看\n4. `workflow-skill` — 可能是工作流/技能编排，值得看\n5. `codex-tokens-compress` — 更像 AGENTS 规范/上下文压缩实验，偏研究工具\n6. `fireworks-tech-graph` — 名字像技术图谱/多智能体平台，但要核实，虽然星高，未必和你要的方向完全一致\n7. `wow-harness` — 看名字像 agent harness / skill tooling，值得核实\n8. `claude-code-setup` — 更像 Claude Code 环境配置，不一定是编排平台，但可能有参考价值\n\n**高度可疑/大概率噪声的：**\n9. `Crimson-Desert-Save-Editor-Mod-For-PC`\n10. `Free-FL-Studio-25.2.5-PC-Edition`\n\n这两个从名字就很不像你前面给的分类，像是：\n- 游戏修改器/存档编辑器\n- 盗版软件分发页伪装仓库\n通常不建议纳入候选。\n\n如果你愿意，我下一步可以直接帮你做其中一种：\n\n**A. 快速筛选**\n我去逐个看 README，给你输出：\n- 是否真是 Agent/MCP/工作流项目\n- 技术栈\n- 是否值得接入 OpenClaw\n- 风险点\n\n**B. 只挑最值得看的前 5 个**\n我直接帮你缩成一个 shortlist。\n\n**C. 生成对比表**\n按这几个维度整理：\n- 项目定位\n- 是否支持多 Agent\n- 是否支持远程调用\n- 部署复杂度\n- 和 OpenClaw 的结合方式\n- 推荐级别\n\n如果你要，我现在就可以继续帮你**逐个核实这 10 个仓库**。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0f0b5ea2d081f49a0169dc5828bfb481918795c1732b7a5321\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":30079,"output":552,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30631,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776048160144,"responseId":"resp_0f0b5ea2d081f49a0169dc58227e688191b7e8db0a3b791018"}}
