{"type":"message","id":"fc82ad37","parentId":"56451b49","timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:26:37.437Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_L539yyJJUuqAXkfcnoGU5jcG|fc_04d32a2e2b8fe5760169dcc4db55048191a224959980a3f67e","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-doc/SKILL.md","offset":1,"limit":40},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-doc/SKILL.md\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":40}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":162,"output":59,"cacheRead":37888,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38109,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776075990886,"responseId":"resp_04d32a2e2b8fe5760169dcc4da576c81918672cc7b1063955f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f4e4bec2","parentId":"fc82ad37","timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:26:37.455Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_L539yyJJUuqAXkfcnoGU5jcG|fc_04d32a2e2b8fe5760169dcc4db55048191a224959980a3f67e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: feishu-doc\ndescription: |\n  Feishu document read/write operations. Activate when user mentions Feishu docs, cloud docs, or docx links.\n---\n\n# Feishu Document Tool\n\nSingle tool `feishu_doc` with action parameter for all document operations, including table creation for Docx.\n\n## Token Extraction\n\nFrom URL `https://xxx.feishu.cn/docx/ABC123def` → `doc_token` = `ABC123def`\n\n## Actions\n\n### Read Document\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"read\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\" }\n```\n\nReturns: title, plain text content, block statistics. Check `hint` field - if present, structured content (tables, images) exists that requires `list_blocks`.\n\n### Write Document (Replace All)\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"write\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\", \"content\": \"# Title\\n\\nMarkdown content...\" }\n```\n\nReplaces entire document with markdown content. Supports: headings, lists, code blocks, quotes, links, images (`![](url)` auto-uploaded), bold/italic/strikethrough.\n\n**Limitation:** Markdown tables are NOT supported.\n\n### Append Content\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"append\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\", \"content\": \"Additional content\" }\n```\n\n\n[172 more lines in file. Use offset=41 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776075997450}}
{"type":"message","id":"95321c80","parentId":"f4e4bec2","timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:26:42.901Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6dc2M4xCavvHFbikAH9lca7a|fc_09f3ab730512bd520169dcc4e0540481918a670ece0f9449cc","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"runtime":"acp","mode":"run","thread":false,"agentId":"codex","task":"Reply with exactly: ACP_OK","timeoutSeconds":45},"partialJson":"{\"runtime\":\"acp\",\"mode\":\"run\",\"thread\":false,\"agentId\":\"codex\",\"task\":\"Reply with exactly: ACP_OK\",\"timeoutSeconds\":45}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":396,"output":47,"cacheRead":38016,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38459,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776075997456,"responseId":"resp_09f3ab730512bd520169dcc4df5e7c8191a6fdacf78d48ee09"}}
