{"type":"message","id":"df23e99f","parentId":"5c939e3d","timestamp":"2026-04-13T12:46:26.853Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 你好，我在。  \n要继续刚才的 **Codex Code 接通排查**，还是直接开始做 **诊所电子处方系统**？","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0eea2fe9a847ec7c0169dce579779c8191841690459e36b276\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":39169,"output":43,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39212,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776084340043,"responseId":"resp_0eea2fe9a847ec7c0169dce5770d5081919ca0f85603962646"}}
